metadata.name: #1 - TWH - "ONNA-BUGEISHA" TOMOE
metadata.description:
I named her Tomoe Gozen.

Tomoe Gozen fought with his lover Minamoto no Yoshinaka during the Genpei war, and her exploits are told in the great war novel about this war, the Heike monogatari. 

It is said that she was fearless and very good in battle. Highly respected by the men, she was one of the main captains of Yoshinaka during the war and led his troops in battle.
